import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class About extends Component { render() { return (
About Me

Who Am I?

I am a graduate student from Lviv Polytechnic National University (NU LP).I love exploring new tools, technologies and meet new people on my way.

I joined SoftServe family a few months ago, and begining of this journey was amazing. I have met a great new friends here, even became a Google Cloud Sertified engineer

What I do?

Here are some of my expertise

Cloud Engineering

I have experience building cloud architectures on Google Cloud, setting up persistent databases, configuring virtual networks etc

Data Structures & Algorithms

As coming from the CS background, I have good grasp over fundamental concepts of DSA

Dev Ops

I am pursuing my internship with DevOps team at SoftServe and working with tools like Jenkins, Docker, Kubernetes and Openshift

I use Telegram eight hours a day :)
